title: LOADING MY GT BLACK SERIES TO THE USA! World Travels Continue
description: My AMG GT Black Series is going to the United States! It's my first experience loading a car into a container, in this case at the docks in Southampton bound for the USA. The epic adventure will kick off with Car Week, and who knows, it might be the only Shmeemobile there!|Back in March, when I packed up my GT Black Series in Dubai I hinted that I'd love to get it at some point over to the USA, and while it might have missed Gumball 3000, that's not going to stop the fun with some huge plans in store. First up, we need to get it loaded up and that means a trip down towards the port so it can be loaded into a container ready for the sailing across the Atlantic Ocean.|Fresh from a run at Supercar Driver's Secret Meet with some awesome track laps at Donington Park, we're kicking off from @The Shmuseum for a last drive in the GT Black Series on UK tarmac... for the time being. The car has already visited Dubai and Abu Dhabi, but now it will visit a new continent - making it the first Shmeemobile to touch down on 3 continents, and with plenty of miles in store during a visit to travel the United States.|What about the Zenvo you ask? I've made no secret that I'd love the Zenvo TSR-S to also be out in the USA, and if that happens it will be beyond insane! For the time being, they are two totally separate movements, the GT Black Series is going for a full cross country tour, with the TSR-S maybe joining it if all is complete and ready to do so. The plan is to drive the GT Black Series on a huge tourist trip around the country, and I know it's going to be extraordinary, as well as the perfect car for the purpose.|Special shout out to MyCarImport for their help sending this car in the opposite direction to my Shelby GT500 that they are currently importing into the UK. It's funny timing to be doing these two cars in opposite directions, but it will all work out very well.|Thanks for watching, Tim|Chapters:|00:00 Intro|01:30 Transport Preparations|04:52 On the Road|05:48 Why the AMG GT Black Series?|07:59 Where is it Going in the US?|09:21 What About the Zenvo TSR-S?|10:54 Drive Continues|11:57 Inflating Tyres|13:07 Fuel Situation|13:51 Transport Costs|17:12 Dropping Off|17:49 Loading into a Container|21:19 Wrap Up|#Mercedes #AMG #Transport||||Subscribe: http://bit.ly/Shmee150YT||Website: http://www.shmee150.com||Shop: http://shop.shmee150.com||Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/shmee150||Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/shmee150

title: Uber lobbied top politicians at undeclared meetings, leaked files show - BBC News
description: Thousands of leaked files have exposed how Uber courted top politicians, and how far it went to avoid justice.|The documents were leaked to the Guardian, and shared with the International Consortium of Investigative Journalists and a number of media organisations including BBC Panorama.|They reveal how a $90m-a-year lobbying and public relations effort recruited friendly politicians in undeclared meetings to help in its campaign to disrupt Europe's taxi industry.|The company denies its lobbying was secret and the ministers say rules were followed.|They also show how the taxi firm's former boss personally ordered the use of a "kill switch" to prevent raiding police from accessing computers.|Uber said its "past behaviour wasn't in line with present values" and it is a "different company" today.|Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#BBCNews

title: [FULL] Terkuak Fakta Alasan Brigadir J Ditembak Bharada E: Istri Kadiv Propam Dilecehkan Brigadir J
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Karo Penmas Divisi Humas Polri Brigjen Ahmad Ramadhan kembali menjelaskan alasan sebenarnya terjadinya baku tembak antar polisi di rumah Kadiv Propam Irjen Ferdi Sambo pada Jumat (8/7/2022) lalu. ||||"Seperti yang saya jelaskan peristiwa itu terjadi Brigadir J memasuki kamar pribadi Kadiv Propam. Di saat itu istri kadiv propam sedang istirahat."kata Karo Penmas Divisi Humas Polri Brigjen Ahmad Ramadhan, Senin (11/7/2022). ||||Brigjen Ahmad Ramadhan kemudian menjelaskan adanya teriakan dari istri Kadiv Propam yang mengundang Tanya Bharada E yang tengah menjaga keamanan di rumah itu. ||||Baca Juga Kronologi Brigadir J Ditembak Polisi Bharada E di Rumah Irjen Ferdy Sambo di https://www.kompas.tv/article/307946/kronologi-brigadir-j-ditembak-polisi-bharada-e-di-rumah-irjen-ferdy-sambo||||"Kemudian Brigadir J melakukan tindakan pelecehan dan juga menodongkan pistol ke kepala Kadiv Propam. Sontak ibu Kadiv Propam berteriak minta tolong. Akibat teriakan tersebut Brigadir J panik."jelasnya. ||||Setelah mendengar teriakan itu Bharada E menghampiri Brigadir J dan bertanya ada apa?||||Saat itu dijelaskan situasinya jaraknya kurang lebih 10 meter dari kamar istri Kadiv Propam.||||"Namun direspons dengan tembakan dilakukan Brigadir J. Akibat tembakan tersebut terjadilah baku tembak. Dan Brigadir J tertembak dan meninggal dunia."jelas Ahmad Ramadhan dalam konferensi persnya.  ||||Baca Juga Polri Usut Motif Brigadir J Masuk Rumah Pejabat Polri, HIngga Ditembak Bharada E di https://www.kompas.tv/article/307963/polri-usut-motif-brigadir-j-masuk-rumah-pejabat-polri-hingga-ditembak-bharada-e||||Berdasarkan olah TKP, saksi dan alat bukti ada 7 proyektil yang dikeluarkan Brigadir J da nada 5 proyektil dari pistol Bharada E.||||Akibat penembakan ini proses pemeriksaan terhadap Bharada E tetap dilanjutkan. ||||Sedangkan jasad Brigadir j sudah dibawa ke keluarganya di Jambi. ||||Lebih lanjut kasus ini berjalan, ditangani Polres Jakarta Selatan. ||||Video Editor: Febi Ramdhani|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/308047/full-terkuak-fakta-alasan-brigadir-j-ditembak-bharada-e-istri-kadiv-propam-dilecehkan-brigadir-j

title: Ja Morant confidently claims he'd 'cook' Michael Jordan one-on-one | NBA | FIRST THINGS FIRST

title: Bodycam Shows Florida Police Chase & Tase Suspect After He Allegedly Struck a Car In His RV
description: The Marion County Sheriff's Office in Florida released bodycam footage showing police chasing a man driving an RV and tasing him after a foot chase on March 20, 2021. Authorities say the man driving the RV struck another vehicle and fled when an officer attempted to pull him over. The suspect eventually ditched the RV and began fleeing on foot. title: â€˜No loan despite making Pak danceâ€¦â€™: Sharifâ€™s minister threatens IMF amid economic crisis | Watch
description: In a bid to save its cash-strapped economy, Pakistan is now training guns at International Monetary Fund. Pakistan's Federal Minister for Interior Rana Sanaullah said that the IMF did not release the tranche for the $6 billion bailout package under its Extended Fund Facility even though "it made us dance to its tune." He added that the Shehbaz Sharif government had even accepted terms "which we were not in favour of". He then urged the international lender to release the tranche without delay so the country could get out of the "difficult situation" it is in. title: Kronologi Brigadir J Ditembak Polisi Bharada E di Rumah Irjen Ferdy Sambo
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Karo Penmas Divisi Humas Polri Brigjen Ahmad Ramadhan membenarkan adanya kejadian penembakan antar anggota polisi di rumah Kadiv Propam Polri Irjen Ferdi Sambo. ||||Brigjen Ahmad Ramadhan mengatakan polisi atas nama Brigadir J tewas ditembak Bharada E di Kompleks Polri Duren Tiga, Jakarta Selatan (Jaksel), Jumat (8/7/2022), pukul 17.00 WIB.||||"Saya akan menyampaikan informasi terkait penembakan di mana peristiwa itu benar telah terjadi pada hari jumat 8 juli 2022, kurang lebih jam 17 atau 5 sore."kata Brigjen Ahmad Ramadhan.||||Ia pun menjelaskan peristiwa singkatnya kepada media pada Senin (11/7/2022). ||||Baca Juga Polisi Bongkar Oplosan Elpiji Bersubsidi, Pelaku Bikin Rugi Negara Hingga Miliaran di https://www.kompas.tv/article/307754/polisi-bongkar-oplosan-elpiji-bersubsidi-pelaku-bikin-rugi-negara-hingga-miliaran||||"Saat itu saudara Brigadir J berada atau memasuki rumah salah satu pejabat Polri di perumahan dinas Duren Tiga, kemudian ada anggota lain atas nama Bharada E menegur dan saat itu yang bersangkutan mengacungkan senjata kemudian melakukan penembakan dan Bharada E itu menghindar dan membalas tembakan terhadap Brigadir J. Akibat penembakan yang dilakukan Bharada E itu mengakibatkan Brigadir J meninggal dunia,"jelasnya. ||Kini kasus ditangani Propam Polri dan Polres Metro Jakarta Selatan. ||||Sedangkan jenazah sudah dibawa ke keluarganya di Jambi untuk dimakamkan. ||||Sedangkan untuk motif penembakan masih didalami dengan diamankannya Bharada E untuk dimintai keterangan lebih lanjut. ||||"Motif penembakan masih didalami, kasus itu akan didalami sebab brigadier J memasuki rumah tentunya barada E yang melakukan karena melakukan pembelaan terhadap serangan dari beigadir J sebelumnya."jelas Karo Penmas Divisi Humas Polri Brigjen Ahmad Ramadhan.||||Video Editor: Febi Ramdhani|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/307946/kronologi-brigadir-j-ditembak-polisi-bharada-e-di-rumah-irjen-ferdy-sambo

title: Squirrels given contraception to limit birth rate  - BBC News

title: Russia cuts off gas to Germany: Will they switch it back on? | DW Business
description: Russian gas firm Gazprom is scheduled to switch off its largest natural gas pipeline running to Germany for annual maintenance. The question is whether Russia will switch it back on. Officials in Germany and across the EU are warning utilities and companies to brace for a possible complete stop to gas flows even after the 10-day repair-period. They fear Russia will use maintenance as a pre-text. Moscow has already reduced flows into Germany in recent weeks, cutting back supply to 40 percent of normal levels while citing repair needs.|The Nord Stream stoppage also appears to be pushing the German government to undermine its own sanctions regime. At Berlin's request, Canada has now temporarily waived its export restrictions on a gas turbine that Siemens was repairing at its facilities in Montreal. Delivery and installation of the turbine, which Russia says is critical to restoring gas flows, could force the EU to partially lift its own sanctions on Russia.
